metadata.fieldPath: root.Auto reload [If you change the config and save the file the plugin will reload itself].Auto reload [If you change the config and save the file the plugin will reload itself]
metadata.description: If you change the config and save the file the plugin will reload itself
metadata.tooltip:
If enabled, the plugin automatically reloads when you save the config file.
Useful for testing changes without restarting the server.

Examples: true, false
